-- MOVES-Evanston Capital hires Lance Donenberg as head of strategic business development
-- By Anannya Pramanick
-- Tue Oct 21, 2014 10:25AM EDT
-- None



Oct 21 (Reuters) - Investment adviser Evanston Capital Management hired Lance Donenberg as the principal and head of strategic business development.

Donenberg joins Evanston Capital from Man Group Plc, where he served as co-head of North America and head of business development.